title: Manna's Bio Bistro
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Catering
description: Organic bistro opened Jan 2015 in the heart of Eimsbüttel, Hamburg. Serves vegetarian food with items including soups, chili sin carne, kebab, a deli case of antipasti and salads plus various cakes and dessert. Vegan items are labelled.
